DTSTART:20260420T203000Z
DTEND:20260420T223000Z
SUMMARY:Euro Truck Simulator 2 | Ep. 11 - Somewhere in Europe... Progress
 Is Happening
DESCRIPTION:Back on the open roads! We're making progress... slowly,
 steadily, and with at least one questionable turn along the way. Travel
 across Europe as king of the road, a trucker who delivers important cargo
 across impressive distances! With dozens of cities to explore, your
 endurance, skill and speed will all be pushed to their limits.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PpsZbPtnMfk
CATEGORIES:Euro Truck Simulator 2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23072211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260401T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260423T175300Z
DTSTART:20260422T203000Z
DTEND:20260422T223000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered | Ep. 10 - Brandenburg Gate
DESCRIPTION:Precision and patience return. One well-placed shot can change
 everything... or alert absolutely everyone. In the dark days of the end of
 World War 2 amidst the ruins of Berlin, one bullet can change history...
 Elite sniper Karl Fairburne returns to the front line in the remaster of
 this award-winning stealth-action experience. Packed with new features,
 contemporary visuals and definitive content.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rpEogWbzhSE
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23082211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260402T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260423T175300Z
DTSTART:20260423T203000Z
DTEND:20260423T223000Z
SUMMARY:Final Fantasy Mystic Quest | Ep. 1 - The \"Easy\" Final Fantasy...
 Is It Actually Good?
DESCRIPTION:A brand-new retro adventure begins! We're diving into a
 classic RPG with a reputation - let's find out if it lives up to it. Step
 into one of the most unique entries in the Final Fantasy series with Final
 Fantasy Mystic Quest, known in Europe as Mystic Quest Legend. Originally
 released on the SNES, this classic RPG was designed as an accessible
 introduction to the genre-making it perfect for both newcomers and retro
 fans.\n\nJoin me as I explore its colorful world, battle iconic monsters,
 and rediscover a game that often flies under the radar in the Final
 Fantasy lineup. With its simplified mechanics, memorable soundtrack, and
 nostalgic 16-bit charm, Mystic Quest offers a laid-back RPG experience
 that's all about fun and exploration.\n\nWhether you played this back in
 the day or you're seeing it for the first time, come hang out, relax, and
 enjoy some retro vibes as we journey through this hidden gem together.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
CATEGORIES:Final Fantasy Mystic Quest
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23092211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260403T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260423T175300Z
DTSTART:20260424T203000Z
DTEND:20260424T223000Z
SUMMARY:Red Dead Redemption II | Ep. 11 - Cold Mornings, Hot Lead, No Peace
DESCRIPTION:Back to the frontier where every decision matters. Tension,
 storytelling, and a world that never really lets you rest. Arthur Morgan
 and the Van der Linde Gang are outlaws on the run. With federal agents and
 bounty hunters massing on their heels, the gang must rob, steal, and fight
 their way across the rugged heartland in order to survive.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
CATEGORIES:Red Dead Redemption II
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
